Robert is the founder of the Messenger Network and teacher of a powerful manifesting process called The Habit of Attraction.  Robert's mission is to help people find their message and then share it with the world using the power of the internet and technology.  The flagship training the Messenger Network is the Full-Time Messenger (FTM) Training.  This program takes a messenger from their current place to becoming a FTM in 6 to 12 months, generating incredible abundance and changing lives around the world with their message.  Robert teaches online programs, creates technologies, and is now putting on live events that facilitate the goal of activating more and more full-time messengers. 
